{"tid":1052252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網紅？】英女皇首次IG發文 16小時有超過20萬個讚","createTime":"2019-03-08T07:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T16:26:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4299cd0688c64e44394386b1e6813f4c3fc15034","tid":1052252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190308/large/1552027803_2297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190308%2Flarge%2F1552027803_2297.jpg&h=4f9e4a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n92歲英女皇伊利沙白二世(Queen Elizabeth II)終於玩IG？其實一直在名為The Royal Family的Instagram都可以看到英女皇的蹤影，不過都是她被拍的相片及影片，今次她就第一次自己用iPad撳掣發文！16小時已經有超過20萬個讚，似乎可以考慮做網紅喎！<br />\n<br />\n昨日3月7日，英女皇去了倫敦科學博物館Science Museum出席活動，今次她就用iPad發了兩張相及一篇文，兩張相就是一封在19世紀，數學家、電腦先驅Charles Babbage寫給Prince Albert的一封信。在Instagram更有影片，看到她撳iPad出文一刻！"},{"pid":"fb40957ccab9205adc42d3314ec88a8b44ad4149","tid":1052252,"uid":76710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3e2dbfdd67d6f4d9f75658db2d8644d3d5d7fc","tid":1052252,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"Her Majesty The Queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}